data.description: Welcome to the Gardens at Cypress Lakes! This charming home has so much to offer. Open floor plan with inviting foyer leading to the living room with a cozy fireplace, large kitchen with eat in dinning featuring granite countertops, island, and pantry. Primary suite downstairs with a spacious walk-in closet, dual sink vanity, garden tub, and separate standing shower. Two guest bedrooms, full guest bath, and laundry room round out the first floor. The second floor opens to a loft space boasting a 2nd fireplace,  built in shelving, and 2 guest bedrooms and guest bath. Relax on the back patio in the privacy fenced backyard or enjoy the community amenities such as the pool, splash pad, and park- located right across the street! Convenient to shopping, restaurants, and an easy commute to Fort Liberty. Schedule your showing today.
